b4244f67-3753-48de-ba1d-c38a5953049d.title: Sir Amik Varze
b4244f67-3753-48de-ba1d-c38a5953049d.text:
I am the leader of the White Knights of Falador. Why
do you seek my audience?

options.text: I don't, I'm just looking around.

e73d8094-a061-4fa2-8f95-5ec3ec418667.title: <player>
e73d8094-a061-4fa2-8f95-5ec3ec418667.text: I don't, I'm just looking around.

4c31d61a-e793-4d54-8b1a-fe9f3a92d4f0.title: Sir Amik Varze
4c31d61a-e793-4d54-8b1a-fe9f3a92d4f0.text:
Well, I need some spy work doing but it's quite
dangerous. It will involve going into the Black Knights'
fortress.

options.text: 遰 I laugh in the face of danger!
I go and cower in a corner at the first sign of danger!

f2e3ba60-315a-4d32-be3e-a073b231e301.title: <player>
f2e3ba60-315a-4d32-be3e-a073b231e301.text: I go and cower in a corner at the first sign of danger!

a4a93f88-bf57-468e-84c4-08e09c65ad5e.title: Sir Amik Varze
a4a93f88-bf57-468e-84c4-08e09c65ad5e.text:
I... suppose spy work DOES involve a little hiding in
corners.

options.text: Oh. I suppose I'll give it a go then.
No, I'm not ready to do that.

2adb6f7a-87e9-4883-9a4f-fbe34ab353c5.title: <player>
2adb6f7a-87e9-4883-9a4f-fbe34ab353c5.text: No, I'm not ready to do that.

05c9bfff-2d6f-4584-a8b1-e9731e031709.title: Sir Amik Varze
05c9bfff-2d6f-4584-a8b1-e9731e031709.text: Come see me again if you change your mind.

82d0c1c6-018e-495f-b844-ac1cd7fbf39e.title: <player>
82d0c1c6-018e-495f-b844-ac1cd7fbf39e.text: Oh. I suppose I'll give it a go then.

51264903-357e-4803-85f6-14b750c563d8.title: Sir Amik Varze
51264903-357e-4803-85f6-14b750c563d8.text:
You've come along at just the right time actually. All of
my knights are already known to the Black Knights.

970af7ce-3660-4596-bc0b-0aed650ec0d6.title: Sir Amik Varze
970af7ce-3660-4596-bc0b-0aed650ec0d6.text: Subtlety isn't exactly our strong point.

79b25c6a-62cb-4954-bb43-fe91429f493b.title: <player>
79b25c6a-62cb-4954-bb43-fe91429f493b.text:
Can't you just take your White Knights' armour off?
They wouldn't recognise you then!

46367f9b-68ad-4862-9696-90d67b0ee0c7.title: Sir Amik Varze
46367f9b-68ad-4862-9696-90d67b0ee0c7.text:
I am afraid our charter prevents us using espionage in
any form, that is the domain of the Temple Knights.

357789be-0937-416b-a392-d40598c28833.title: Sir Amik Varze
357789be-0937-416b-a392-d40598c28833.text:
That information is classified. I am forbidden to share it
with outsiders.

c3f239dc-0824-4963-a0ea-18bb9a47fa6b.title: <player>
c3f239dc-0824-4963-a0ea-18bb9a47fa6b.text: So... what do you need doing?

ddea00c9-4009-4d86-bc65-f0e42c60369e.title: Sir Amik Varze
ddea00c9-4009-4d86-bc65-f0e42c60369e.text:
Well, the Black Knights have started making strange
threats to us; demanding large amounts of money and
land, and threatening to invade Falador if we don't pay
them.

8ce81e75-18db-4f6d-aad0-3db7885d78c9.title: Sir Amik Varze
8ce81e75-18db-4f6d-aad0-3db7885d78c9.text: Now, NORMALLY this wouldn't be a problem...

59f078ee-10af-43e5-8f08-4a1770fda286.title: Sir Amik Varze
59f078ee-10af-43e5-8f08-4a1770fda286.text: But they claim to have a powerful new secret weapon.

056c0c9e-95a7-464f-8f00-938a7477961a.title: Sir Amik Varze
056c0c9e-95a7-464f-8f00-938a7477961a.text:
Your mission, should you decide to accept it, is to
infiltrate their fortress, find out what their secret
weapon is, and then sabotage it.

3fed8e6f-db4e-429d-bc53-6fdc5c7fcf10.title: Start the Black Knights' Fortress quest?

463efa03-334b-459f-b4ec-966990579856.title: <player>
463efa03-334b-459f-b4ec-966990579856.text: I laugh in the face of danger!

7738758d-8167-4a79-96d4-efef31ab71fc.title: Sir Amik Varze
7738758d-8167-4a79-96d4-efef31ab71fc.text: Well that's good. Don't get too overconfident though.

cbebef63-a908-47e9-9ef6-9238159735c7.title: Sir Amik Varze
cbebef63-a908-47e9-9ef6-9238159735c7.text:
Good luck! Let me know how you get on. Here's the
dossier for the case, I've already given you the details.

e6cf910c-63f1-42c7-8d27-f65cb59dcc9a.title: <player>
e6cf910c-63f1-42c7-8d27-f65cb59dcc9a.text:
I haven't managed to find what the secret weapon is
yet...

9514d989-3484-48ec-a712-0b19c396ca6c.title: Sir Amik Varze
9514d989-3484-48ec-a712-0b19c396ca6c.text: Well, keep at it! Falador's future is at stake!

8d00fec8-1e36-45a7-9c06-1d886ff63056.title: Sir Amik Varze
8d00fec8-1e36-45a7-9c06-1d886ff63056.text: Here's the dossier on the case.

8889b775-c50d-4557-85a8-07455a2577e6.title: <player>
8889b775-c50d-4557-85a8-07455a2577e6.text:
I've found out what the Black Knights' secret weapon
is. It's a potion of invincibility.

d5898328-1a74-4020-b758-a5de0492720b.title: Sir Amik Varze
d5898328-1a74-4020-b758-a5de0492720b.text:
A potion of invincibility? That is grave news indeed. If
you can sabotage it somehow, you will be very well paid.

19f48f2d-d011-4a40-bc50-69929752fa86.title: <player>
19f48f2d-d011-4a40-bc50-69929752fa86.text:
So when I finish this mission for you can I be a white
knight? Can I wear your armour too?

b978b312-5d23-4ace-a5d1-a50f57af895c.title: Sir Amik Varze
b978b312-5d23-4ace-a5d1-a50f57af895c.text:
I am afraid I cannot authorise you to become a white
knight unless under a situation of dire circumstance.
Assisting us on a freelance basis will be well worth your
time however and you will have my personal gratitude.

693a6cc7-c338-4cbf-ab62-c20b65c39edd.title: <player>
693a6cc7-c338-4cbf-ab62-c20b65c39edd.text: I can't buy stuff with personal gratitude though...

21888f3e-dfb0-4809-9e50-8ed14a1906df.title: Sir Amik Varze
21888f3e-dfb0-4809-9e50-8ed14a1906df.text:
There is of course also the financial recompense as I
said.

c619a736-3a17-416c-963b-4db4511a5e44.title: <player>
c619a736-3a17-416c-963b-4db4511a5e44.text: Ok! I'll get on to sabotaging that potion.

57b6d558-0eeb-4382-b23e-85d7989868a0.title: Sir Amik Varze
57b6d558-0eeb-4382-b23e-85d7989868a0.text:
Yes, we have just received a message from the Black
Knights saying they withdraw their demands, which
would seem to confirm your story.

a974b95c-4ea6-4f5f-a9af-3ad4f83306d0.title: <player>
a974b95c-4ea6-4f5f-a9af-3ad4f83306d0.text:
I have ruined the Black Knights' invincibility potion.
That should put a stop to your problem and an end to
their little schemes

b61bea22-058b-4f22-b9c3-a929fc6e9d04.title: <player>
b61bea22-058b-4f22-b9c3-a929fc6e9d04.text: Now I believe there was some talk of a cash reward...

ae1576c3-8f0c-471d-b2d8-18bb17c93c30.title: Sir Amik Varze
ae1576c3-8f0c-471d-b2d8-18bb17c93c30.text: Absolutely right. Please accept this reward.

8bd5c36b-a8cb-4b76-8948-f84c20610f33.title: <player>
8bd5c36b-a8cb-4b76-8948-f84c20610f33.text: Do you have any other quests for me to do?

72015b1e-e428-40c4-81c0-49cf6df6e15a.title: Sir Amik Varze
72015b1e-e428-40c4-81c0-49cf6df6e15a.text: Nothing I can think of at the moment...
